OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHillsborough Law would     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25F'level scales of justice', 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fsays mayor                 
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A Hillsborough Law is needed to ensure 
OL,6, fairer treatment for bereaved families,
OL,7, Liverpool City Region's mayor has said.
OL,9,FSteve Rotheram and Greater Manchester  
OL,10,FMayor Andy Burnham said the government 
OL,11,Fneeds to "level the scales of justice".
OL,13,FThey are calling for measures          
OL,14,Frecommended in a 2017 report, based on 
OL,15,Fthe experiences of Hillsborough        
OL,16,Ffamilies, to be enshrined in law.      
OL,18,FThe government said it would engage    
OL,19,Fwith bereaved families and "carefully  
OL,20,Fconsider the points of learning".      
